quoteText: If you are in the European Union, Switzerland, or other regions with laws governing data collection and use, you acknowledge that edX and each Member may transfer, process and store your personal information in the United States and other countries, the privacy laws of which may be considered less strict than those of your region.
title: The court of law governing the terms is in a jurisdiction that is less friendly to user privacy protection.
